data.description: Welcome home to this well maintained beautiful Ranch home. Easy living with one level living, No steps & a level driveway. Move in ready with New roof, freshly painted interior, and renovated kitchen. Kitchen features white cabinets, new quartz countertops, new backsplash, new sink, & new s/s dishwasher. Plenty of room for large table or an additional island. Living room has a fantastic cathedral ceiling that allows tons of natural light and is perfect for entertaining. Master bedroom boasts a private en-suite with white cabinetry and new quartz. The other 2 bedrooms offer carpet, ceiling fans, and sizable closets. Relax in your private fenced in level backyard with a lovely patio. Community offers swim/tennis/pickle-ball courts, beautiful park & playground facilities. This home is minutes to shopping, fitness, dining and highly acclaimed schools. Quick & easy access to Hwy 92, GA 400, & I-575.
